{"tid":2275396,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台工會批政府完美示範何謂「無良僱主」","createTime":"2020-11-07T06:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T06:51:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f24f61fcaf390689ba4d887273b0d3a1f11decdf","tid":2275396,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"香港電台電視節目《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被捕，警方指她將車牌查冊資料用於不符聲明指的用途，涉嫌違反《道路交通條例》。蔡玉玲以服務提供者形式受聘，並非公務員。公務員事務局表示，公務員事務局沒有權限批准支援服務提供者。香港電台節目製作人員工會感到極度失望。<br />\n<br />\n港台工會表示，雖然感到極度失望但屬意料之內，質疑副廣播處長馮建業有否向公務員事務局要求豁免，亦不滿港台隸屬的商務及經濟發展局置之不理，批評當局完美示範何謂「無良僱主」。<br />\n<br />\n港台工會又指，自僱合約員工亦屬港台員工，如有關員工因工作惹上官非，管方應提供一切協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558835-20201107.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558835-20201107.htm&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuKha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=7f703614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558835-20201107.htm&h=3f3566aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558835-20201107.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c104b21921878b74afc2a1f404c037121be63eef","tid":2275396,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"721又唔見拉"},{"pid":"354c528c270dc77202c43d2dac05c6f91c40c096","tid":2275396,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654a5f5a66c15b049d3d4c652e907af3b33c96dd","tid":2275396,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"626408f02e4710841c7ddc76581640a6619dafba","tid":2